<div class="offcanvas offcanvas-end" tabindex="-1" id="offcanvasRight" aria-labelledby="offcanvasRightLabel">
  <div class="offcanvas-header p-3 text-center">
    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="offcanvas" aria-label="Close"></button>
  </div>
  <div class="offcanvas-body">
    <h5 class="offcanvas-title my-5" id="offcanvasRightLabel">About magr.</h5>

    <div class="container">
      <h5 class="mb-4">An intermediate Ruby On Rails Developer based in Bordeaux, France.</h5>
      <p>My journey into the tech world began with a curiosity to <b>understand how websites work</b>, and it quickly turned into a lifelong commitment to creating intuitive, <b>user-centric</b> digital experiences.</p>
      <p>I specialize in building responsive websites using technologies like <b>Ruby on Rails, JavaScript, ReactJs and Bootstrap.</b></p>
      <p>My approach combines creativity with technical skills, ensuring <b>every project is not only functional but also visually engaging.</b></p>
    </div>
    <div class="container my-5">
      <div class="mb-3">
        <p class='mb-4'>You can explore my journey in the language of your choice:</p>
        <%= link_to '/resume_melissa_augier_eng.pdf', class: 'c-btn', target: '_blank' do %>
          <span class="c-btn__label">
            open resume in english
            <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M6 2H14L20 8V20C20 21.1 19.1 22 18 22H6C4.9 22 4 21.1 4 20V4C4 2.9 4.9 2 6 2Z" 
                    stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M14 2V8H20" 
                    stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M9 15H15M9 19H15" 
                    stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        <% end %>
      </div>
  
      <div>
        <%= link_to '/resume_melissa_augier_fr.pdf', class: 'c-btn', target: '_blank' do %>
          <span class="c-btn__label">
            open resume in french
            <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M6 2H14L20 8V20C20 21.1 19.1 22 18 22H6C4.9 22 4 21.1 4 20V4C4 2.9 4.9 2 6 2Z" 
                    stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M14 2V8H20" 
                    stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M9 15H15M9 19H15" 
                    stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        <% end %>
      </div>

      <h5 class='mt-5 mb-4'>On the hunt for exciting opportunities</h5>
      <p>I’m always looking for new opportunities to learn, grow, and share my skills. Whether it’s collaborating on exciting projects, tackling new challenges, or exchanging knowledge with others, I’m eager to connect and contribute.</p>
      <p>Feel free to reach out!</p>
      <div class="mt-3 mb-5">
        <%= mail_to 'augiermelissa@gmail.com', class: 'c-btn' do %>
          <span class="c-btn__label">
            send me an email →
          </span>
        <% end %>
        <p class="small">* email : augiermelissa@gmail.com</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-about text-white p-3 text-center">
      <p class="m-0">
        &copy; <%= Time.current.year %> magr. All rights reserved. 
        <span class="mx-2">|</span>  
        <%= link_to "LinkedIn", "https://www.linkedin.com/in/melissaaugier", class: "text-white text-decoration-none" %>  
        <span class="mx-1">•</span>  
        <%= link_to "GitHub", "https://github.com/melissaaugier", class: "text-white text-decoration-none" %>
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
